track.name: Look What You Made Me Do

album.title: Look What You Made Me Do

wiki.summary: "Look What You Made Me Do" is about looking back at the various struggles someone has faced, and how they have risen above every challenge and conflict to become smarter and harder than before. The song is a reminder of how much someone can grow from their experiences and how they can transition from being a victim to becoming a survivor of any situation. The song is also a reflection of the power of resilience and refusing to become a victim of someone else's schemes and manipulations. Read more on Last.fm.
